00:43:48,507 --> 00:43:49,910
Estamos em um bar

511
00:43:49,911 --> 00:43:52,653
<i>ao sul do cruzamento
com a 290.</i>

512
00:43:52,654 --> 00:43:55,219
290. Entendido.

513
00:44:02,262 --> 00:44:04,020
